data.description: Secluded with your own private circle drive, some might even call this their own slice of paradise! Sitting on over an acre of land in the city limits this home also has views of the field giving that country feel while still being in close proximity to Richland Chambers Lake, the school, shops & dining. The lot in itself is amazing & even has 3 pecan trees, but the house has so much to offer as well. If entertaining is your thing, you will surely have the space for it with this home. There is a sunroom located right off the kitchen that has several windows letting in the natural light and view of the field behind. An added bonus in this home you don't see every day is the green room behind the living room which could be converted into a screened in patio or whatever your heart desires. The wood burning fireplace is the perfect spot to gather around at holidays or during the winter. So many different options throughout this home, you just need to come see it for yourself.
